<i>♪ Que sera sera ♪</i>

06:18.943 --> 06:21.816
<i>♪ What will be will be ♪</i>

06:31.303 --> 06:36.047
<i>♪ Now I have
children of my own ♪</i>

06:36.178 --> 06:38.528
<i>♪ They ask their father ♪</i>

06:38.659 --> 06:42.140
<i>♪ "What will I be?" ♪</i>

06:42.271 --> 06:44.708
<i>♪ "Will I be pretty?" ♪</i>

06:44.839 --> 06:47.058
<i>♪ "Will I be rich?" ♪</i>

06:47.189 --> 06:50.105
<i>♪ I tell them tenderly ♪</i>

